<title>DamageDealerComponent</title><para>Stores damage values indexed by collision layer for O(1) lookup:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>setDamage(float, uint32_t)</computeroutput> - Sets damage for a specific layer</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>damage(uint32_t)</computeroutput> - Returns damage for a specific layer</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Layer IDs must be powers of 2 (bitmask values).</para>
